Description:
Kover was also one of the MANY, MANY,
MANY, MANY, MANY, MANY rebels that Donk
took hostage; Doctor Yoko decided to
modify his body and digestive system with
guitar strings for some strange reason that I don't even
know anyting about. Anyways, he later
escaped and got his revenge by beating
Yoko up till he was unconcious, and sneaking
out. Hes furious all the time, but damn does that guy make
good omelettes.
